sentence: Among the underlying components of the S&P 500 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Salesforce.com Inc (Symbol: CRM), where a total of 26,325 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 2.6 million underlying shares.
That amounts to about 52% of CRM's average daily trading volume over the past month of 5.1 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $160 strike call option expiring July 26, 2019, with 1,777 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 177,700 underlying shares of CRM.
